22:54.152 --> 22:55.434
Maybe with the next book.

22:55.454 --> 22:56.776
You think you do that?

22:56.936 --> 22:59.661
Doris Lessing did that.

22:59.841 --> 23:00.602
Yeah, yeah.

23:00.642 --> 23:02.605
