23:02.625 --> 23:03.847
Right, right, exactly.

23:06.411 --> 23:07.092
But I...

23:07.763 --> 23:09.712
I... What's the thing now?

23:10.138 --> 23:10.483
Um...

23:11.138 --> 23:15.442
Well, I guess you hit the hidden self in the fiction, I guess.

23:15.602 --> 23:19.526
So where could people who know you find you in your work?

23:19.546 --> 23:22.109
Well, that's a secret.

23:22.549 --> 23:26.433
Let me tell you, when I do these, I'm always looking for my lead.

23:26.593 --> 23:28.535
I'm always looking for my kicker.

23:29.476 --> 23:31.077
You just gave me my kicker.

23:31.157 --> 23:31.678
Oh, good.

23:32.319 --> 23:32.499
Okay.

23:32.639 --> 23:36.022
Well, they can find me everywhere and nowhere.

23:36.042 --> 23:36.543
That's great.

23:36.563 --> 23:37.263
That's wonderful.

23:38.004 --> 23:41.027
